{"tid":1734689,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方指理大示威者涉嫌暴動呼籲投降　暫未有攻入逼切性","createTime":"2019-11-18T11:33:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T11:43:07.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3553de29fc17f65cc3686db85a4dabbec8f3e6df","tid":1734689,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:33:48.000Z","msg":"西九龍總區指揮官卓孝業表示，警方昨日至今一直呼籲在理工大學內的示威者自首，指將為傷者提供醫療安排，但校園內有大量燃燒品和爆炸品，警方強行攻入將對雙方造成嚴重傷亡，因此目前沒有攻入校園的逼切性。<br />\n<br />\n他形容武器在示威者手上，選擇權在他們，警方飛虎隊狙擊手有專業訓練，有需要時亦有能力使用。<br />\n<br />\n卓孝業呼籲示威者放下武器立即走出校園投降，指有關人士是涉嫌暴動，會受到公平對待和審訊，強調這也是示威者一直追求的法治，不能妥協。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，理工大學一帶形勢危險，呼籲市民切勿前往，擔心他們將成為示威者的人盾。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493057-20191118.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493057-20191118.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix1QmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=68c6595e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493057-20191118.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6cd1fbb7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493057-20191118.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ce2a5755eb3f35e46effc40c0916f708c1566375","tid":1734689,"uid":337761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T11:34:19.000Z","msg":"Twitter組24時keep住更新<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">幫手retweet+ like + reply</span> <br />\n㩒入----&gt; <a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=O2Kpqs6hAe%2BpM%2F1AUa5ix1QmTevdAkBFS5MHro4yyYg%3D&h=d319f065\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 <span style=\"color: gold;\"> /task3</span> <br />\n<br />\n最新Task分類<br />\n/task1: 法案、抗爭活動<br />\n/task2: BNO、中國、其他香港議題<br />\n/task3: !!!! #PolyU !!!!<br />\n/task4: 日韓德任務"},{"pid":"15f44483f76232ffa6ca3051